{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cf3eb46a-cd5f-4671-9e5d-e67b7a604cdc","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported in MSTest v3**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your settings map to:\n\n| `.testsettings` | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout></MSTest>` |\n| `useLoadContext=\"true\"` | `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>false</DeploymentEnabled></MSTest>` |","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_uBbWkLA0BuQxHPzTMEcV3A","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_sxarBgX1hfaRbD5U3EHwWD","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-7ba8a344a0c74ef4b9d0e06eb480cf34/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>false</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-7ba8a344a0c74ef4b9d0e06eb480cf34/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"bf00fd4f-8d81-4fd3-b2a6-936e720952f6","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has:\n1. A `.testsettings` file with a 30-second test timeout and assembly resolution config\n2. An MSTest v3 project targeting .NET 8\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The migration path is to use a `.runsettings` file instead. Let me create the equivalent `.runsettings` file and explain the migration.\n\nThe `.testsettings` has:\n- `TestTimeout` of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n- `AssemblyResolution` with `useLoadContext=\"true\"` - this controlled test deployment/loading behavior\n\n\n- For the `.runsettings` equivalent, I need to map the timeout to the `<MSTest>` section and set `DeploymentEnabled` to false since the `useLoadContext` setting indicates tests should load from the test directory without deployment. Now I'll create the `.runsettings` file.","outputTokens":592},"id":"3f491947-b74f-4af7-8ca6-c86c0ce2a9a6","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:13:22.034Z","parentId":"34fba00a-29e9-4992-8d78-f4d1b8dd47a1"}
